          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "AUN Prompt Cycler-\n\nEither enter any number of prompts, one per line, or connect a multiline string node with prepared prompts.\n\nEnter a title for each prompt in the format-\n\n'Title:Rest of prompt text.'\n\nThe prompts will be selected with  each run of the workflow, either by manually changing the index, sequentially, or by range of indexes (eg 1,2,4-7), or by a search string (looks for matching search terms in all of the prompts in the list).\n\nThe index can be used to drive other nodes, eg an AUN Lora chooser, as shown here."
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
