          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "AUN Lora by index- (AUNRandomLoraModelOnlyMulti)\n\nThis is a sophisticated lora loader, with the option to automatically select up to 3 loras per prompt (or NONE), the prompts are selected by index. This index can be used to match a selected prompt to its respective loras/trigger words.\n\nThe trained words/triggers can be looked up from Civitai, or from the lora metadata, and auto-enetered as trigger words for each separate lora.\n\nTo edit the loras and other parameters, double click the node body, or right-click for more options, such as show/hide clip strengths.\n\nThe prompt index, prompt title, and current trigger words are displayed in real time.\n"
      ],
      "color": "#2a363b",
      "bgcolor": "#3f5159"
    },
